  "title": "Warehouse Assistant #76429",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Logistics & Supply Chain</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Warehouse Assistant</strong></li><li>Working Location: Kallang</li><li>Working Hours: 5.5 days (Mon - Fri 9.30am -6.30pm, Sat 9.30am - 1pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic Salary up to $2300 + Performance Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent Role</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Help with daily warehouse tasks such as receiving, picking, sorting, packing, loading, and unloading goods.</li><li>Keep the warehouse clean and organized.</li><li>Assist the warehouse team as needed.</li><li>Take part in regular stock counts and inventory checks.</li><li>Follow all safety and security guidelines for warehouse operations.</li><li>Perform other duties as given by your supervisor.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Positive and enthusiastic attitude.</li><li>Able to work efficiently and respond quickly.</li><li>Responsible and reliable.</li><li>Able to perform tasks that may require lifting and moving goods.</li><li>Hardworking and willing to learn.</li><li>Comfortable working in a fast-paced environment.</li><li>Having a forklift licence is an advantage.</li><li>Able to speak, write, and do data entry in Chinese, as the system operates in Chinese.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#76429 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
